Insider Activity


Individual




Lawrence S. Hershfield



Mr. Lawrence S. Hershfield is Chairman at Hawaiian Holdings, Inc., President & Chief Executive Officer at RC Aviation Management LLC, Chief Executive Officer at Ranch Capital LLC, and Chairman at Hawaiian Airlines, Inc. He is on the Board of Directors at Infinity Bio Energy Ltd.
Mr. Hershfield was previously employed as Chairman by Premier Entertainment Biloxi LLC, a Trustee by Stanford University, Chief Executive Officer by FINOVA Group, Inc., President & Chief Executive Officer by PepsiCo International, and President by Leucadia International, Inc. He also served on the board at Berkadia Commercial Mortgage Servicing, Inc.
He received his undergraduate degree from Bucknell University and an MBA from the Stanford Graduate School of Business.



